==English==

===Etymology===
Probably a natural expression, due to its presence with similar meaning in many unrelated languages: for example, Burmese {{term|ဟေး|lang=my|sc=Mymr|tr=hei}}, Finnish {{term|hei|lang=fi}} and Mandarin Chinese {{term|哎|lang=cmn|sc=Hani|tr=āi}}, and various sound-alikes as Roman [[eho]], Greek (''eia''), Dutch [[he]], German [[hei]].

